Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.36,0:03:37.10,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}おはよう世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.10,0:03:40.32,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fsp0}Good Morning World!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.33,0:03:53.81,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}何れ程　歩いたろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.81,0:03:57.78,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}足の痛みだけが
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.78,0:04:00.88,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}その距離を物語る
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.31,0:04:07.97,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}長い夜を越えた絶景への期待が
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.97,0:04:11.14,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}今日　僕を生かしている
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.01,0:04:17.06,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}神々の霊峰　新緑の宮殿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.06,0:04:22.09,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}岩窟の最奥　蒼穹の涯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.09,0:04:27.91,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}踏破してみせる　限界は無い
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.91,0:04:31.20,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}惑星の隅々まで
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.99,0:04:34.86,op-jp,,0,0,2,,{\blur2}おはよう世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.86,0:04:38.10,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fsp0\blur2\pos(640,-4)}Good Morning World!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.10,0:04:42.12,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不可能の闇を祓って
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.12,0:04:47.50,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}神話を日常に変えていく{\fsp0}Odyssey
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.97,0:04:56.70,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一歩ずつ石を穿つ様な　この歩みで
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.25,0:05:01.63,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}世界を拡げよう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.63,0:05:03.63,op-cn,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.36,0:03:37.10,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}早安 世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.10,0:03:40.32,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fsp0}Good Morning World!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.33,0:03:53.81,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我脚步不停
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.81,0:03:57.78,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只有双脚的痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.78,0:04:00.88,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}知晓走过的距离
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.31,0:04:07.97,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我期待着漫漫长夜后的绝美风景
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.97,0:04:11.14,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}活在今天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.01,0:04:17.06,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}神之灵峰 新绿宫殿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.06,0:04:22.09,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}岩窟深处 苍穹尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.09,0:04:27.91,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都要一一到达 永无止境
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.91,0:04:31.20,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我要走遍每一个角落
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.99,0:04:34.86,op-cn,,0,0,2,,{\blur2}早安 世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.86,0:04:38.10,op-cn,,0,0,2,,{\blur2\fsp0}Good Morning World!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.10,0:04:42.12,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}驱散名为不可能的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.12,0:04:47.50,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}将神话变为日常的{\fsp0}Odyssey
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.97,0:04:56.70,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一步又一步 如滴水穿石般
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.25,0:05:01.63,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}拓宽眼前的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.63,0:05:01.63,op-cn,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.83,0:22:42.38,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fsp0}Maybe I don’t know what to do
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.38,0:22:45.05,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fsp0}Hurry up, my mind is on the moon
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.05,0:22:47.34,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fsp0}Flying up to where the wind blew
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.84,0:22:52.09,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,手のひらに溢れてくる　情熱が目を覚ます
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.09,0:22:54.60,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,彷徨っているだけの{\fn黑体\fsp0}This World
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.60,0:22:56.81,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,１つだけ光る君の{\fn黑体\fsp0}Pure
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.81,0:22:58.68,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,錆びたナイフなんかじゃ刺せない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.68,0:23:00.35,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fsp0}I am burning like a fire gone wild
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.35,0:23:02.94,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,心に矢を放たれた瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.94,0:23:05.52,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,まとわりつく雑音が弾けた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.52,0:23:07.74,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fsp0}Everything was different from that moment on
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.74,0:23:10.11,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fsp0}If I don't try ,I'll never know
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.32,0:23:15.53,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,何故　花は咲くのだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.53,0:23:19.83,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,君の声が響くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.83,0:23:20.87,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fsp0}Tell me why？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.87,0:23:22.96,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fsp0}I just shouted to the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.96,0:23:25.88,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fsp0}But you are no no no longer here, that’s right？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.88,0:23:30.17,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,あの日僕ら確かめてた LIFE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.17,0:23:36.14,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,儚い夢と　言われたっていいから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.14,0:23:41.14,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,傷だらけの今日から救い出すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.06,0:00:01.06,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.83,0:22:42.38,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,或许我正不知所措
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.38,0:22:45.05,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,快一点 我的心已飞向月球
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.05,0:22:47.42,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,乘上轻风 四处飞舞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.84,0:22:52.09,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,热情已经苏醒 从我掌中溢出
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.09,0:22:54.60,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,这个世界漫无目的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.60,0:22:56.81,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,唯有你的纯真光芒四射
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.81,0:22:58.68,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,生锈的刀根本无法刺入
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.68,0:23:00.35,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,我如烈火般熊熊燃烧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.35,0:23:02.94,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,心中忽而中箭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.94,0:23:05.52,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,世界瞬间安静
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.52,0:23:07.74,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,自那时起 一切都不同以往
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.74,0:23:10.11,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,若不尝试 我将不得而知
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.32,0:23:15.53,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,花儿为什么会绽放
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.53,0:23:19.83,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,你的声音响起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.83,0:23:20.87,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.87,0:23:22.96,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,我朝苍天呐喊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.96,0:23:25.88,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,你是否永远离开了我？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.88,0:23:30.17,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,那一天 我们见证了生命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.17,0:23:36.14,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,即便那是虚无缥缈的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.14,0:23:41.14,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,我也要从伤痕累累的今天 将其拯救出来
